description:
Danny recaps this week's The Real Housewives of Beverly Hills, which featured Rinna's lip launch, TV dinners with Kath, a Garcelle and Dorit feud, and a new confessional from Collette Reardon. Over on The Real Housewives of New York, we might not be getting a reunion this season. Should we? Unclear.
